Global VCS actions
------------------
VCS Operations Popup... :: Alt+`
Commit...           :: Ctrl+K
Update Project      :: Ctrl+T
Rollback            :: Ctrl+Alt+Z
Push...             :: Ctrl+Shift+K
Next Change         :: Ctrl+Alt+Shift+Down
Previous Change     :: Ctrl+Alt+Shift+Up
Show Version Control window :: Alt+9
Show Commit window  :: Alt+0
